        "new_string": "## API Server Setup and Integration\\n\\n**staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/server/config.go**:\\n- **Config** struct has AdmissionControl field (admission.Interface)\\n- AdmissionControl is stored in REST handler context\\n- Used to process all requests through the admission pipeline\\n\\n**staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/server/options/admission.go**:\\n- **AdmissionOptions** struct holds plugin names, config file paths, decorators\\n- **ApplyTo()**: Creates admission chain using Plugins.NewFromPlugins(), wraps with metrics decorator, applies it to server config\\n- RecommendedPluginOrder: [NamespaceLifecycle, MutatingAdmissionPolicy, MutatingAdmissionWebhook, ValidatingAdmissionPolicy, ValidatingAdmissionWebhook]\"",
